longBusinessSummary: Candles Scandinavia AB (publ) manufactures and sells scented candles based on plant-based wax made of rapeseed oil. It distributes candles under private labels, such as Yankee Candle, WoodWick, Blanche, Olivia & Co, Millefiori Milano, and Leyonore, as well as own brands. Candles Scandinavia AB (publ) was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Örebro, Sweden.
